## 1. Product overview
### 1.1 Document title and version
- PRD: [Project/Feature Title]
- Version: 1.0

### 1.2 Product summary
[2-3 short paragraphs providing an overview of the project or feature.]

## 2. Goals
### 2.1 Business goals
- [Bullet list of business objectives]

### 2.2 User goals
- [Bullet list of what users aim to achieve]

### 2.3 Non-goals
